        <h1 style = "font-family:arial;font-size:40px;font-style:bold"><b>INTRODUCTION</b></h1>

        <p>Welcome to the Notre Dame of Dadiangas University, Inc. This Privacy Policy is about our policy in terms of collecting, using, or processing your personal data, in regards to your engagement with the University.</p>
        <p>We respect your right to privacy and strive to abide by all applicable privacy and data protection regulations, including the Data Privacy Act of 2012 (DPA). We, like the National Privacy Commission (NPC), strive to strike a balance between your personal privacy and public safety. Regarding the free flow of information, particularly while pursuing our legitimate interests and fulfilling our obligations as an educational institution, employer, and/or contracting partner.</p>
