        <h2 style = "font-family:arial;font-size:28px;font-style:bold;margin-bottom:30px">PRIVACY POLICY FOR UNIVERSITY PERSONNEL</h2>
           
        <p><b>WHAT</b> – We gather your personal information in a variety of ways. Written documents, picture, and digital content may be included. Here are several examples:</p>
        
